      <title>FBI Director to resign. And, UHC CEO killing brings attention to U.S. life expectancy</title>
      <author>Brittney Melton</author>
      <link>https://www.npr.org/2024/12/12/g-s1-37879/up-first-newsletter-fbi-director-christopher-wray-luigi-mangione-health-care-life-expectancy</link>
